{"tid":2143950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海逸酒店集團將動員旗下2千多名員工參與病毒測試","createTime":"2020-08-07T11:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T12:03:14.000Z","uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d901832b65394b6bbe06e0e0607fe1ae28287c","tid":2143950,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:23:46.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥宣布將免費為全港市民進行新型冠狀病毒檢測。長實旗下海逸國際酒店集團表示對政策深表支持，集團正了解病毒檢測計劃詳情，將動員旗下15家酒店合共約2500名員工積極參與。海逸說，相信進行病毒檢測可以讓員工安心以及為顧客提供信心，亦可望加強抗疫成效，有助本地旅遊、酒店及餐飲等行業早日復蘇。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-07 19:07:35<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542451-20200807.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542451-20200807.htm&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=9ca1827b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542451-20200807.htm&h=57dc3a2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542451-20200807.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n間公司邊個的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56177adc392ed32a66c3c857e104540e0227100d","tid":2143950,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:24:45.000Z","msg":"測左唔會傳染咩？"},{"pid":"8c32a2858ad0d1521b014fca703376720e0dd936","tid":2143950,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:24:45.000Z","msg":"DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa346a6d6ff8b73aeb21bee55462b1ff81596de","tid":2143950,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:36:59.000Z","msg":"集體辭職啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（千祈咪做檢測）一人留DNA，全家十八代奶野。廢老做檢測，後生比人拉。<br />\n<a href